manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Dimmable Under Cabinet LED Lighting Kit | Warm White 3000K This Litever plug in 6-Light-Bar Under Cabinet LED Lights Kit is perfect to work as kitchen counter top lighting or under or above kitchen cabinet light. They will bring your kitchen back to life again. Of course, besides kitchen under cabinet lighting, you can find various and diverse applications for this under cabinet lighting kit: storage cabinet lights, curio cabinet, laundry room/garage cabinet light or any other cabinet light, display cabinet light, bookcase lights, bookshelf or any other shelf lights, pantry or hutch cabinet lights, collection showcase lighting, cupboard lights, task lights for work bench, over head desk light, basement lighting etc.

Why Litever Plug-in Under Cabinet LED Lights Kit ? 1. Power Adapter of Higher Power Load. While many other competitors are using a much smaller 24W or even 12W power adapter, this Litever Under Cabinet LED Light Strip Kit adopts a Class 2 Certified 36W power adapter. Higher power load allows us to make the LED light bars of higher power and thus brighter LED light bars.Plus, this higher power load power adapter allows you to add extra LED light bars to this Litever 6-Light-Bar Under Cabinet Lights Kit to match different layouts. 2. More Reliable Power Adapter of Longer Lifespan. While many others are using power adapters of standard components and can only last for maximum 6000~8000 hours (or even less), Litever choose power adapters adopting more reliable core electrical components (capacitors) and can last for more than 20,000 hours. Many others are saying that LED lights can last for more than 50,000 hours. Actually, that’s not true.Though the LED light strips or bars (as well as the dimmer or cables) themselves actually can last for more than 50,000 hours indeed, the power adapter, which feeds them, can NOT last for 50,000 hours.Many others are using power adapters of lifespan less than 6000 hours but still declaims that their lights can last over 50,000 hours. 3. Extendable and Easy to DIY to Match Your Cabinet Layouts. Many other similar under cabinet lights are NOT extendable at all. Or, they do not sell extra parts for DIY. However, following "Recommended Layout", you can buy extra LED light bars, extension cables, power splitters to add into this Litever Under Cabinet Lights Kit for DIY. Plus, you can buy Litever compatible motion sensor switches or door-activated switches to DIY them into motion activated or door-activated lighting kits for more applications, i.e, closet lights, safe lights, wardrobe lights, night lights, etc.

Slim But Super Bright Under Cabinet LED Light Kit. Delivering Soft Even Warm White Light. NOT compatible with existing wall dimmers. With professional compact low profile and easy installation design, this under cabinet LED lighting kit is perfect to be installed for kitchen cabinets, over counters, under shelf, bookcase, closets, etc. Thanks to the diffused light cover, this cabinet light bar delivers very soft, even but bright warm white light. No LED dots, no light glaring. Very slim cabinet LED lighting bars with slim cables/connectors. Easy to hide them by the lips of the kitchen cabinets.Super bright branded LEDs adopted. CRI >80. Very nice light color.Dimmable 10~100% ONLY with the included LED dimmer. NOT compatible with existing wall dimmers.Dimmer with "Memory" function. It will remember your last setting, even in case of power-off. You can plug the power adapter into a smart plug to turn the power adapter ON-OFF by your smart plug and still get the previous setting.Modular design. Easy to install.Aluminum PCB. Aluminum housing. Robust and sturdy.

If you want to DIY this Litever LED lights kit into "Motion Activated" lights for safe box, closets, wardrobes, cabinets, pls kindly search "B0B62N5MV1" or "B09B9QFRFQ" on amazon.com for compatible PIR motion sensors.If you want to DIY this Litever LED lighting kits into "Door Activated" lighting kits for safe box, closets, wardrobes, pls kindly search "B0B5ZRKQV2" on amazon.com for compatible door-control switches.

Where to Install Litever Under Cabinet Lighting Kit Kitchen Under or Over Cabinet Lights Perfect to work as kitchen under cabinet / over cabinet lighting. Shelf Lighting & Above Cabinet Decoration Lighting Litever under cabinet lighting is perfect to work as shelf lighting. Also good to be installed as above cabinets lighting. Display Cabinet Lighting It's perfect to work as task lighting for display cabinets for your collections.
